
    Press q to quit:

    Keyboard shortcuts in main window (* use digits):

        a) Create/Add links to the Audio list *   │ n) Launch ncurses mpv tui
        b) Show main window bindings              │ p) Load/Download a collection playlist *
        c) Edit your mpmrc file *                 │ q) Quit mpv
        d) Access the default playlist *          │ r) Refresh main window when mpv has been stopped
        e) Edit a playlist from your collection * │ s) Save a tmp list or remove a collection playlist *
        f) Load local folder/files *              │ t) When mpv is running, display the song/video title
        h) Go to previous song                    │ u) Show help screen
        j) Stop or quit mpv                       │ v) Create/Add links to the Video list *
        k) Toggle play/pause                      │ x) Quit mpm
        l) Go to next song                        │ z) Clear all tmp lists *
        m) Manuals & help access                  │ Ctrl+B) change themes, Ctrl+M) mpmrc quick view
        ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    Shortcuts in the "mpm player" if mpvc_tui is set to native (uses fzf).

        Enter:       play selected item.
        Lelf arrow:  seek 30s backward.
        Right arrow: seek 30s forward.
        Ctrl+N:      play next item.
        Ctrl+P:      play previous item.
        Ctrl+T:      toggle pause.
        Ctrl+R:      Restart the playlist from the beginning.
        Ctrl+X:      quit mpv (stop) and go back to main menu.
        Escape:      exit mpvc tui interface.